				<div class="main" id="main" role="main" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
	<meta itemprop="url" content="http://www.pcworld.com/article/2028588/crash-proof-computer-tactic-revealed-by-uk-researchers.html" />
	<div class="imageContainer580xX"><figure id="page-lede" class="oneUp"><img  class="largeImage " src="http://zapt4.staticworld.net/images/article/2013/01/blue-screen-of-death-100021501-large.jpg" itemprop="image" /></figure></div>
			<article>
    
    	<div class="department">		    
			    <a href="/category/computers-all">Computers</a>
		        <ul class="tags">
		        		<li><a href="/tag/security/">Security</a></li>
